Hello Bjarne.

I just tried a build from HEAD and all seems to work fine.  Perhaps your 
order file is from a previous version and the newer code has trouble 
digesting it?  Do you get the below after creating a new crawl job using 
the UI?

(FYI: CVS HEAD is not guaranteed to be stable.)

Yours,
St.Ack
